{"tid":2265353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有市民持白花到太子站外　大批警員戒備","createTime":"2020-10-31T11:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T11:03:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"97d5d8d7e51b44d681388cb47dec1b6db71b7156","tid":2265353,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:03:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557680-20201031.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557680-20201031.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=84ccd1fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557680-20201031.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7307414c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557680-20201031.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n太子站8.31事件發生至今14個月，多名市民包括油尖旺區議會副主席余德寶等，手持白色鮮花在站外，鄰近旺角警署的太子站出口樓梯，亦有人放下鮮花。<br />\n<br />\n大批軍裝及便衣警員在一帶戒備，多輛警車停在附近，警員要求在場記者進入指定範圍。"}]}